OL,5, A father whose son died of cancer -    
OL,6, which a doctor said was likely caused  
OL,7, by gas-flaring from BP's oil fields in 
OL,8, Iraq - told the company that "cancer is
OL,9, so common it's like the flu" at its    
OL,10, annual meeting.                        
OL,12,FAli Hussein Julood documented his life 
OL,13,Ffor a BBC investigation which found    
OL,14,Fhigh levels of cancer-linked pollutants
OL,15,Fin a BP oil field.                     
OL,17,FHe died on 21 April of leukaemia.      
OL,19,FBP said it offered condolences to the  
OL,20,Ffamily.                                
